","tid":349814,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T23:29:29.000Z","msg":"一個經常被抄牌既人好難令人信佢囉"},{"pid":"9ccb08a987b8427f6e5c439e83f0da69a0a8e811","tid":349814,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T23:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個經常被抄牌既人好難令人信佢囉</blockquote><br />\n弱智都唔信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18d3f14c289a0fedc7d6959f1fee8061651c6a3","tid":349814,"uid":2114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:04:21.000Z","msg":"點解會揀訪問佢<br />\n係咪之前有幾多新聞？<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解硬係有少少妄想嘅味道 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0790f0e48e50b96d67ef1b5ac4e5e913a561c87","tid":349814,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:08:06.000Z","msg":"當自己係乜"},{"pid":"4c13adfbb96c6a3ecee9bf8fad05181ffa31414c","tid":349814,"uid":43619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:56:48.000Z","msg":"呢條友係出名的網上騙子<br />\n成日話自己有7000會員，原來入WhatsApp group就當人會員<br />\n演唱會街飛炒黃牛就話係vip飛加手續費<br />\n又話識明星結果d名星逐個踢爆佢講大話<br />\n又自稱有十二個教練牌，點知打波衰過初哥"},{"pid":"c9a76e3f364a7e2bad745dedc271a3e220f3c3cb","tid":349814,"uid":43619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:04:58.000Z","msg":"佢叫林偉麟alan,  網上一早已經有佢九大罪狀連罪證的懶人包<br />\n<br />\n１炒賣演唱會門票；並將與明星合照放上facebook，假扮明星朋友騙人購買黃牛貴票<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱話/90448/體育會賣演唱會飛-五月天門票380炒至950元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F90448%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E6%9C%83%E8%B3%A3%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E9%A3%9B-%E4%BA%94%E6%9C%88%E5%A4%A9%E9%96%80%E7%A5%A8380%E7%82%92%E8%87%B3950%E5%85%83&d=7uKelBNRfzH3e%2FejPrgbUv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0b1e71a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱話/90448/體育會賣演